---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Emergency Light Tester" description="Privacy Policy for Emergency Light Tester Android App">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="reveal text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="reveal text-gray-500 italic mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          Emergency Light Tester ("the App") is developed by NtroniQ. This privacy policy explains how we handle your data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Data Collection</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-4">
          The App stores the following data locally on your device only:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Location names and zones you create</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Test records and results</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> Tester names and signatures</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-pink mr-3">&#8226;</span> App settings and preferences</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Data Storage</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          All data is stored locally on your device. We do not collect, transmit, or store any of your data on external servers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-4">
          The App uses the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-pink mr-3 mt-1">&#8226;</span> <span><strong>Firebase Crashlytics</strong> - Collects anonymous crash reports to help us fix bugs. This includes device type, operating system version, and crash stack traces. No personal data is collected.</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-pink mr-3 mt-1">&#8226;</span> <span><strong>Google Play Billing</strong> - Processes in-app purchases. Payment information is handled entirely by Google.</span></li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          We do not sell, trade, or share your personal data with third parties.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Data Deletion</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          You can delete all app data at any time by clearing app data in your device settings or uninstalling the App.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          The App is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-navy mb-6">
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact: <a href="mailto:privacy@ntroniq.com" class="text-pink hover:text-pink-light">privacy@ntroniq.com</a>
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
          &copy; 2026 NtroniQ. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
